          "question": "What are the Project tools are available outside of the Portal?",
          "answer": "XWiki, Guacamole, Jupyterhub, Superset, and the Command Line Tool are available for Project Members to use. Talk to your Project Administrator about setting up these tools if they are not yet configured for your Project."
        },
        {
          "question": "What is XWiki?",
          "answer": "XWiki is a structured wiki that can be used by Project Members for documentation, knowledge sharing, and collaboration."
        },
